<tr><td colspan=2><font face="verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica" size="2">ATLANTA -- Online Insight, which provides CRM applications designed to enable companies to understand the preferences of their customers, said it has appointed Gregory Koutrelakos as vice president of business development. Mr. Koutrelakos has served as executive vice president of sales and marketing at Ivex Corporation and senior business development manager at Oracle.<br><br>The company is backed by Greystone Capital Group.
