<tr><td colspan=2><font face="verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica" size="2">AUSTIN, TEXAS -- Amicus, a provider of IP-based financial software, said it has appointed Powell Crowley as vice president of marketing. Mr. Crowley formerly served as CEO of Visionary Media and CEO of South Hills Datacom. He was also general manager of Asia Pacific for Micro Warehouse and director of marketing for Inmac.<br><br>The company is backed by individuals and Stellent. </font><br><br>
