<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td>&#8226; <a name="vwQNQLLQIIJI"><b><font face='arial,helvetica' size="2">Magnum Technologies Names C.S. Mondelli VP Sales & Marketing</font></b></a></td><td align="right"><a href="#vwQNQLLQIIJIx"><img src="http://venturewire.com/images/arrow.gif" border="0" height="11" width="11" alt="top"></a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://people.venturewire.com/o_mailer.asp?sid=QNQLLQIIJI" target=NEW><img src="http://venturewire.com/images/mail2.gif" border="0" height="10" width="15" alt="mail"></a>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><font face="verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica" size="2">MINNEAPOLIS -- Magnum Technologies, which develops network- and system-management applications designed to monitor and safeguard IT performance and network and system reliability, said it named C.S. Mondelli as its first executive vice president of sales and marketing. Previously, Mr. Mondelli served as president and CEO of Transition Networks. He will report to president and CEO, Greg Crow. Magnum Technologies is backed by Hitachi, Holland Capital Group, Portage Equity Investments, Space Center Ventures, StarTec Investments, and individual investors. </font><br><br>
<a href="http://www.magnum-tech.com" target="_new"><font face='arial,helvetica' size='2'>http://www.magnum-tech.com</font></a>
</td></tr></table><br>
