<tr><td colspan=2><font face="verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica" size="2">TORONTO -- Atelier America, an art publishing and marketing firm, said it promoted Paul Stainton as its first director of direct and Web marketing. Mr. Stainton joined Atelier America in April from CBC to work on Atelier America&#39;s online marketing program. Atelier America is backed by Blackburn Group and Direct Equity Partners. </font><br><br>
